<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="x-ua-compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/lib/bootstrap.min.css">
    <!--<script type="text/javascript" src="./public/javascript/libs/jquery-3.1.0.min.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="./public/javascript/libs/bootstrap.min.js"></script>-->

    <!--内联样式表-->
    <style type="text/css">
        #total {
            min-height: 600px;
            background-color: #4D6DAD;
            background: -webkit-linear-gradient(to bottom, #4D6DAD, #214d80);
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #4D6DAD, #214d80);
            color: rgb(236, 236, 236);
            height: auto;

            -webkit-transform: scale(1.03);
            -moz-transform: scale(1.03);
            -ms-transform: scale(1.03);
            -o-transform: scale(1.03);
            transform: scale(1.03);

            -ms-word-wrap: break-word;
            word-wrap: break-word;
            word-break: break-all;
        }

        .total-border {
            background-color: #d2d2d2;
            background: -webkit-linear-gradient(to bottom, #aaaaaa, #214d80);
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #efefef, #c8c8c8);

            border-bottom: solid 2px #e86930;
        }

        .content a {
            color: #d2d2d2;
        }
        .content a:hover {
            color: #8cb5ff;
        }

        /* 标题 */
        .head {
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-shadow: 5px 5px 3px #395980;
            color: #ecf3f4;
        }

        /* 内容 */
        .content {
            font-size: 1.5em;
        }

        .copyright a {
            color: #FFFFFF;
        }

        /*文字特效*/
        .box1 {
            text-shadow:
                    0px 0px 0 rgb(188,178,188),1px 0px 0 rgb(173,163,173),
                    2px 0px 0 rgb(157,147,157),3px 0px 0 rgb(142,132,142),
                    4px 0px 0 rgb(126,116,126),5px 0px 0 rgb(111,101,111),
                    6px 0px 0 rgb(95,85,95), 7px 0px 0 rgb(79,69,79),
                    8px 0px 7px rgba(0,0,0,0.35),8px 0px 1px rgba(0,0,0,0.5),
                    0px 0px 7px rgba(0,0,0,.2);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<!--header-->
<%- include admin_header.ejs%>

<!--主要内容-->
<div class="total-border">
    <div class="container" id="total">
        <!--判断请求内容-->
        <% if (content == "about") { %>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12 head">
                <p><h1><%= title %></h1></p>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-12 content">
                <p><h3 class="box1">服务条款</h3></p>
                <ul>
                    <li>使用本站将被视为同意网站所有协议</li>
                    <li>GuideFishing提供的是合法的网络视频,音乐,图片等内容</li>
                    <li>网站由个人开发,托管于腾讯免费云主机</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-12 content">
                <p><h3 class="box1">帮助中心</h3></p>
                <ul>
                    <li>如果网站侵犯了您的个人权益请发邮件至: yangwei13@outlook.com 进行申诉</li>
                    <li>如需反馈请发送邮件至:yangwei13@outlook.com</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-12 content">
                <p><h3 class="box1">免责声明</h3></p>
                <ul>
                    <li>用户应该遵守相关的法律法规</li>
                    <li>资源均来源于网络公开和个人用户上传,网站不负产权责任</li>
                    <li>网站享有监督权,可以删除非法的资源</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <% } %>

        <% if (content == "contact") { %>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12 head">
                <p><h1><%= title %></h1></p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12 content">
                <p><h3 class="box1">加入团队</h3></p>
                <ul>
                    <li>期待您的加入!</li>
                    <li>联系QQ:1334239104</li>
                    <li>联系邮箱:yangwei13@outlook.com</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-12 content">
                <p><h3 class="box1">建议反馈</h3></p>
                <ul>
                    <li>反馈信息请包括反馈主题和反馈内容,必要的话请给出您的联系方式.</li>
                    <li>反馈请至邮:yangwei13@outlook.com</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <% } %>

        <% if (content == "follow") { %>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12 head">
                <p><h1><%=  title %></h1></p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12 content">
                <p><h3 class="box1">Github</h3></p>
                <ul>
                    <li>我的主页: <a href="https://github.com/NoJsJa">https://github.com/NoJsJa</a></li>
                    <li>GuideFishing项目主页: <a href="https://github.com/NoJsJa/node-GuideFishing">https://github.com/NoJsJa/node-GuideFishing</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-12 content">
                <p><h3 class="box1">新浪微博 & Twitter</h3></p>
                <ul>
                    <li>微博: @AuTuMn_愤怒的Node</li>
                    <li>Twitter: @Johnyou29734209</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <% } %>
    </div>
</div>

<%- include admin_footer.ejs %>
</body>
</html>
